flowchart LR
    A([Live Stream URL]) --> B[Stream Resolver\nstreamlink + yt-dlp]
    B --> C[ffmpeg Chunker\n10-second rolling chunks]
    C --> D[Chunk Queue\nThread-safe queue.Queue]

    D --> E[Audio Extraction\nper chunk WAV]
    E --> F[faster-whisper\nnear real-time STT]
    F --> F2[Transcript Aligner\ntimestamp fix + sentences]

    D --> G[Frame Extraction\nSSIM per chunk]
    G --> H[DIP Enhancement\nper chunk]
    H --> I[OCR / Captioning\nper chunk]

    F2 --> J[Chunk Accumulator\nmerge aligned + visual\nwith time offset]
    I --> J

    J --> K{Every 30s?}
    K -->|Yes| L[Fuser\nfused.json updated]
    L --> M[LLM Summarizer\nrolling mode]
    M --> N[Output Formatter\nformat all outputs]
    N --> O[rolling_summary.json\nfor UI polling]
    O --> P[Streamlit UI\n3-second auto-refresh]

    K -->|No| J

    Q([Stop Signal\nfrom UI or Ctrl+C]) --> C
    Q --> R[Final Pass\nfull summarize + format]

    style A fill:#4CAF50,color:#fff
    style O fill:#2196F3,color:#fff
    style P fill:#9C27B0,color:#fff
    style Q fill:#f44336,color:#fff
